        <updateDate>2017-12-19T22:45:26Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><strong>Pharmaceutical Information Exchange Act</strong></p> <p>This bill amends the Federal Food, Drug, and Cosmetic Act to&nbsp;allow information about&nbsp;a new&nbsp;investigational medication or the investigational use of a medication&nbsp;approved&nbsp;by the Food and Drug Administration&nbsp;to be provided to health care entities if the information is based on reliable scientific evidence.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
    <title>Pharmaceutical Information Exchange Act</title>
    <titles>
